          "text": "Major technology companies are shifting focus from ever-larger language models to smaller, efficient alternatives. Industry analysts report that compact models now match flagship systems on common benchmarks while cutting inference costs by up to 80 percent. Early enterprise adopters cite faster deployment and reduced operational complexity as key benefits.",
